data.text:
Party Pop is the third mainstream album by Gummibär that was released under the label of Gummybear International on October 16th, 2015. It is a compilation album of fan favorite Gummibär songs, with around 15 tracks plus a bonus track.

The physical album was earlier sold before its official release date as an exclusive item at VidCon 2015. It also features a mini-poster inside with coloring page.
